---
title: Italian Sausage Tortilla Involtini with Spinach Salad
description: This dish's balance of sweet, savoury and creamy cheesiness will drive you wild! Fragrant Italian sausage is blended with tomatoes and veggies, then wrapped in soft tortillas. These involtini are a match made in heaven. Enjoy!
